label.profile:
Planet Mu was started in 1995 as an imprint on [l=Virgin] on which to release µ-Ziq and other, similar artists.
When it turned out that Virgin didn't do well in marketing this kind of music, [a=Mike Paradinas] set up the label independently in 1998. This is where the [b]ZIQ...[/b] catalog numbers start.
